ord-Znajek-powered jet. We associate the hard prompt spike with the\nquasispherical breakout of the jet from the disk wind. As the jet plows through\nthe wind with subrelativistic velocity, it creates a radiation-dominated shock\nthat heats the wind material to tens of kiloelectron volts, producing the soft\nthermal component.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Oct 2017 16:58:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 18:03:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 15:15:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-23"}
