ad spectral peaks that we observe starting at 2.5 d after the merger. These\ndata provide direct evidence that binary neutron star mergers are significant\nproduction sites of even the heaviest r-process elements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Oct 2017 16:57:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-17"}
