 ultra-high energy neutrino-nucleus\ncross-sections, and for future high-energy lepton-proton colliders such as the\nLHeC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Oct 2017 18:00:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Mar 2018 13:40:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-09"}
