on of\nthe boundary layer at the top of the roughness elements as well as to a\nmodification of the temperature field in between the obstacles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Oct 2017 11:03:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2018 13:17:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-17"}
